            <span class="block">Your Website Sells</span>
            <span class="block text-yellow-300 mt-2">More Cars</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl">{description}</p>

          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">The car buyer story:</p>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-sm">Buyer searching for "2023 Toyota Camry near me" visits 15 dealership websites. 13 have outdated inventory, poor photos, no pricing, difficult contact. 1 modern site with current vehicle listings, detailed photos, price transparency, easy test drive scheduling. Guess which gets the visit? For auto sales, professional website = legitimate dealership = trust = visits. Current inventory = real dealer = cars sold.</p>
